data.description: Panoramic views on this cozy and charming walk-out-ranch-style home perched on a ridge, overlooking the Big Thompson River with full mountain views. Enjoy the sunset from your spacious balcony deck. The home has Hickory floors, 2 primary suites, powder bath and an office on the main level, as well as large kitchen island, stone surround fireplace in living room, all with large windows and natural light. Kitchen offers gas cooktop w/double oven and touch screen command center. Walk-out basement presents incredible views as well as a kitchenette, 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom with rough in for another primary suite or multi-generational living. This over 1/3-acre lot is beautifully landscaped with fence on 2 sides in addition to this home the oversized 3 car garage has gas hookup for heat and 220-amp service.  This home won't last long, close to Scheel's, I-25, and Loveland.
